<!--监护人授权页面-->
<view class="auth-container">
  <view class="auth-header">
    <image class="auth-icon" src="/images/auth-shield.png" mode="aspectFit"></image>
    <view class="auth-title">监护人授权与隐私保护确认</view>
  </view>

  <view class="auth-content">
    <view class="auth-section">
      <view class="section-title">为什么需要授权？</view>
      <view class="section-text">
        为保护未成年人隐私，我们需要在收集学生信息（年级、班级、实践照片等）前获得您的授权。
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="auth-section">
      <view class="section-title">我们会收集哪些信息？</view>
      <view class="info-item">
        <text class="info-icon">📝</text>
        <text class="info-text">基本信息：年级、地区、学校、昵称</text>
      </view>
      <view class="info-item">
        <text class="info-icon">📞</text>
        <text class="info-text">联系方式：手机号（用于课程通知）</text>
      </view>
      <view class="info-item">
        <text class="info-icon">📷</text>
        <text class="info-text">活动照片：实践活动中的照片</text>
      </view>
      <view class="info-item">
        <text class="info-icon">🎓</text>
        <text class="info-text">学习记录：投票、活动参与记录</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="auth-section">
      <view class="section-title">隐私保护承诺</view>
      <view class="promise-item">
        <text class="promise-icon">✓</text>
        <text class="promise-text">所有信息均经过加密存储</text>
      </view>
      <view class="promise-item">
        <text class="promise-icon">✓</text>
        <text class="promise-text">照片仅限本班级或授权用户可见</text>
      </view>
      <view class="promise-item">
        <text class="promise-icon">✓</text>
        <text class="promise-text">不会向第三方提供学生信息</text>
      </view>
      <view class="promise-item">
        <text class="promise-icon">✓</text>
        <text class="promise-text">可随时申请删除个人数据</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="protocol-links">
      <text class="link-text" bindtap="viewProtocol" data-type="privacy">《未成年人隐私保护协议》</text>
      <text class="link-text" bindtap="viewProtocol" data-type="authorization">《社会实践活动授权书》</text>
    </view>

    <view class="checkbox-container">
      <checkbox-group bindchange="onCheckboxChange">
        <label class="checkbox-label">
          <checkbox value="agree" checked="{{isAgreed}}" color="#4A90E2"/>
          <text class="checkbox-text">我已阅读并同意上述协议，我是监护人，同意授权</text>
        </label>
      </checkbox-group>
    </view>

    <button 
      class="btn-confirm {{isAgreed ? 'btn-primary' : 'btn-disabled'}}" 
      bindtap="confirmAuthorization"
      disabled="{{!isAgreed}}">
      确认授权
    </button>

    <view class="tip-text">
      * 一次授权，全系统生效。除非注销账号，否则无需重复授权
    </view>
  </view>
</view>

